[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0875","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1023","title":"Oracle Solaris useradd 账户过期日期校验绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 的 useradd 命令在处理 \"-e\" 参数指定的账户过期日期时，未能正确解析特定日期格式，导致账户过期后仍允许用户登录。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 系统，攻击者需拥有有效账户且账户已过期，通过设置特定日期格式绕过过期限制继续登录系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，属于中等严重程度的权限绕过漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1023"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.613","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 7.0 补丁 106327-01 或更高版本（Solaris 7 推荐补丁簇），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。若无法立即升级，可编辑 /etc/default/useradd 设置 INACTIVE=0 禁用账户过期功能，或通过 /etc/shadow 手动锁定过期账户（passwd -l 用户名）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92904175406756&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/426","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/df06113bb625f86b49f1950d55874a29f8e76a55/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1023","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1023.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_110869.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris26_110883.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5805d482-63b1-4dfb-8afc-b26b682a9546.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0775","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9133,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10820}}","description":"运行 IOS 的思科千兆交换机和路由器在访问控制列表（ACL）中对 \"established\" 关键字存在不当处理，导致网络访问控制机制被绕过。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标设备发送特制的 TCP 数据包，利用该漏洞让设备转发原本被 ACL 规则拒绝的未经授权数据包，从而绕过防火墙或路由器的访问控制策略。该漏洞影响运行 IOS 的思科千兆交换机及路由器系列产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0775"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.957","remediation":"升级受影响的 Cisco 千兆交换机/路由器至修复了该 ACL \"established\" 关键字处理缺陷的 IOS 版本（如 11.2(15)GS 及以上、12.0 系列对应修复版本），通过思科 Software Center 下载并安装官方 IOS 镜像；在无法立即升级时，临时修改访问控制列表，移除或重寫存在缺陷的 \"established\" 规则，改用基于状态的 CBAC 防火墙检查，并在边界过滤非法入站 TCP 数据包作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0775","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8981d7e7baa3f6c5d7a90cd823433b0422b8fcd2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0775.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0775","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0775.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4cacb08131e7c4736ad136de17873dbcaeddf850/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0775.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vjxr-fvc6-86qw/GHSA-vjxr-fvc6-86qw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0775.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000670.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87022/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1231","title":"SSH SSH 用户枚举漏洞","description":"SSH 2.0.12 及可能其他版本在用户认证过程中存在信息泄露漏洞。服务端对有效用户名与无效用户名的处理逻辑存在差异：有效用户名可多次尝试输入密码，而无效用户名仅提示一次即断开连接。未经认证的远程攻击者可通过发送大量 SSH 认证请求，根据服务器响应模式（是否提示输入密码而非立即拒绝）来枚举目标系统上存在的用户账户名。该漏洞虽不直接导致代码执行或权限提升，但枚举出的有效账户为后续暴力破解、密码喷洒或社会工程攻击提供了精准目标，显著降低了进一步攻击的门槛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1231"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.880","remediation":"升级至 OpenSSH 7.9 及以上版本，该版本对所有用户统一返回相同的密码提示次数，避免通过交互差异枚举有效账号。如无法立即升级，可改用键盘交互认证（KeyboardInteractive）替代密码认证，或在 sshd_config 中设置 `MaxAuthTries 1` 并将 `LogLevel VERBOSE` 以记录异常枚举行为作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14758","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2276","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1231","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7g97-5hq7-x7mm/GHSA-7g97-5hq7-x7mm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87557/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/1999.tsv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0457d271-b4c6-4bb2-813d-1cf71d06fee5.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000668.txt","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/7cddb9480dac0125b9b2b00c91d6226d5d995ec7/1999/CVE-1999-1231.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1134","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1134.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1496","title":"Debian Linux 及 Red Hat Sudo 1.5 文件存在性信息泄露漏洞","description":"Sudo 1.5 版本存在本地信息泄露漏洞。本地攻击者可通过尝试将目标文件名作为程序执行来探测任意文件是否存在，当文件不存在时系统会返回不同的错误提示信息，从而泄露文件存在性信息。该漏洞影响 Debian Linux 2.1 和 Red Hat 6.0 等系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，利用条件较为有限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1496"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.947","remediation":"升级 Sudo 至 1.6 及以上版本，该漏洞在 Sudo 1.6 中已修复。对于 Debian 系统，升级至 Debian 3.0 及以上版本；对于 Red Hat 系统，升级至 Red Hat 7.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可限制本地用户对 sudo 的访问权限，仅允许受信任用户使用 sudo 命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14665","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/321","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2277"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1134.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1134.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0171","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0493","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.statd RPC调用转发漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 的 rpc.statd 服务存在 RPC 调用转发漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 SM_MON 和 SM_NOTIFY 命令将伪造的 RPC 调用转发至本地操作系统，进而利用该机制触发 automountd 等其他组件的远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0493"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.887","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 2.6 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，可禁用 rpc.statd 服务（`/etc/init.d/rpc stop; rm /etc/rc3.d/S73nfs.client`），或在防火墙层面阻止外部对 RPC 端口 111/TCP、111/UDP 及 rpc.statd 动态端口的访问。同时建议限制 NFS 仅在内网可信网络使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/186&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-99-05-statd-automountd.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-045.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/450","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19327"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1237","title":"Apache smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向使用该库的 Apache::AuthenSmb 等模块发送特制的超长用户名或密码参数触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响所有使用 smbval 认证库的 Web 服务。受影响的系统需升级至修复版本或禁用受影响模块。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1237"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.657","remediation":"立即停止使用 smbvalid/smbval 认证库及 Apache::AuthenSmb 模块，升级至已修复缓冲区溢出问题的 smbvalid 2.0.3 或更高版本。如无法升级，建议迁移至 mod_auth_ntlm_winbind 或 mod_authz_smb 等替代方案，并在输入边界对用户名和密码长度进行严格校验（用户名≤64字节，密码≤128字节），同时以非特权用户运行 Apache 进程以降低利用影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14384","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2272"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0757","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0757.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0970","title":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD visadmin.exe 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD 1.1/2.0 visadmin.exe 拒绝服务漏洞","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0970"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.977","remediation":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD 1.1/2.0 已停止维护，厂商不再发布安全补丁。建议立即停止使用该产品，迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等仍在维护的 Web 服务器。临时缓解措施：在防火墙或反向代理层面限制对 visadmin.exe 的远程访问，仅允许受信 IP 地址连接，并删除或重命名 Web 根目录下的 visadmin.exe 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14311","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1808","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2271","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20304","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0970.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0970","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0970.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0970.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w2hf-w4w7-554m/GHSA-w2hf-w4w7-554m.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/V/visadmin.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0970.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000664.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0757.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0757.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0757.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1101","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1412","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16363,\"outputTokens\":37,\"totalTokens\":16400}}","description":"Apple Mac OS X Server 1.0（版本 10.0）在运行 Apache HTTP 服务器时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标服务器上运行的 CGI 程序持续发送大量的 HTTP GET 请求洪流，即可触发漏洞。由于每个请求都会由 Apache 派生出一个新的 CGI 进程，海量并发请求会在短时间内生成大量进程，耗尽系统资源，最终导致 Apache HTTP 服务器崩溃或系统停止响应。该漏洞影响运行 Mac OS X Server 1.0 并启用 CGI 的 Apache 服务，攻击条件仅为攻击者可访问目标 Web 服务的网络端口，利用方式是通过自动化工具高频请求 CGI 接口造成资源过载。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1412"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.160","remediation":"升级 Apple Mac OS X Server 至 10.0.4 或后续版本以修复 Apache 进程耗尽问题；在 Apache 配置中限制 CGI 进程并发数（如设置 MaxClients 上限）并启用 mod_cgi 请求速率限制；无法立即升级时，可在前端防火墙或负载均衡器上对单个源 IP 的 HTTP GET 请求频率做限流，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14215","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/306","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19244","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-1412.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8057fa2fdc38632692a6b3f836dd95e1eb8504fd/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1412.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1412","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/httpd/CVE-1999-1412.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1412.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/b6ed432383ec9e70047ae649904e3a43ee847c40/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1412.md","https://github.com/ericpattison/Mariner/blob/6b6b870716931ff24c71b575ecd690aa7979fdd6/CBL-Mariner/SPECS/httpd/CVE-1999-1412.nopatch","https://github.com/anchore/nvd-data-overrides/blob/404b484bd5d19c483528cbf4559074858313076b/data/1999/CVE-1999-1412.json","https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded/blob/e93799db0e7c7b23da8a00891403425ae7e87d7b/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1101.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1101.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1098","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1400","title":"经济学人 1999 屏幕保护程序 安全绕过漏洞","description":"The Economist 1999 屏幕保护程序在启用\"密码保护\"选项后存在安全绕过漏洞。具有物理访问权限的攻击者可在屏幕锁定状态下通过运行 Internet Explorer 绕过屏保密码保护，从而读取受保护的文件。该漏洞影响 The Economist 1999 屏幕保护程序版本，攻击者需具备本地物理访问条件，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1400"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:21.577","remediation":"该屏幕保护程序已停止维护，建议立即卸载 The Economist 1999 Screen Saver，改用操作系统自带的屏幕锁定功能（Windows 按 Win+L 锁定）。如必须使用，可在组策略中禁用 Internet Explorer 在锁屏状态下的运行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.indenial.com/hypermail/ntbugtraq/1999/June1999/0007.html","http://archives.indenial.com/hypermail/ntbugtraq/1999/June1999/0009.html","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92851653600852&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/466","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1400.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1400","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1400.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1400.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cw7-fpf7-gx4h/GHSA-7cw7-fpf7-gx4h.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6d096c97-530f-4bd4-aa6f-5cf867018e78.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_bypass.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1063","title":"CDomainFree whois_raw.cgi 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"CDomain Web 服务器中 whois_raw.cgi CGI 脚本存在命令注入漏洞，由于程序未对用户提交的 fqdn 参数中特殊字符进行过滤，远程攻击者可通过向该脚本发送包含 shell 元字符的恶意请求，实现在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 CdomainFree 2.4 及之前版本，攻击无需认证，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1063"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.747","remediation":"建议立即从服务器移除或禁用 whois_raw.cgi 脚本，或升级到 CdomainFree 最新版本。如无法升级，应对 fqdn 参数做严格输入过滤，禁止 shell 元字符（; ` | & $）传入，同时考虑迁移到替代的 Whois 查询方案。若该 CGI 非业务必需，直接删除或注释相关配置即可彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14019","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/304","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2251","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19242","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1063","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1063.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/whois_raw.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2q8x-m9cg-3m3v/GHSA-2q8x-m9cg-3m3v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0546","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0546.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0804","title":"Linux Kernel Linux Kernel 2.2.x ICMP畸形包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2.x 内核在处理 ICMP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。该漏洞源于内核网络子系统对畸形 ICMP 数据包的校验不足，当数据包携带异常的 ICMP 类型（type）、代码（code）以及非法的 IP 头部长度时，内核无法正确解析并可能导致系统崩溃或资源耗尽。攻击者可构造此类特制数据包，通过向目标主机发送该畸形 ICMP 包触发漏洞，无需身份认证且可远程发起。受影响范围主要包括运行 Linux 2.2.x 内核的系统（如 Debian Linux 2.1、RedHat Linux 6.0、SuSE Linux 6.1 等）。利用方式通常为使用工具构造携带异常选项的 IP 报文发送 ICMP 数据包，致使目标系统内核异常、停止响应，从而造成拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0804"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.527","remediation":"建议将受影响的 Linux 2.2.x 内核升级至官方已修复该 ICMP 处理缺陷的 2.2.10 及以上版本；Debian 用户升级到 potato 内核包、RedHat 用户应用对应 RHSA 内核补丁、SuSE 用户升级至 6.1 之后的内核 RPM。若暂时无法升级，可在边界防火墙或用 iptables/route 过滤来源不可信的畸形 ICMP 包，并设置 net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_all=1 缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/302","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19241","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0804.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0804","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0804.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0804.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r76w-gfvq-4v99/GHSA-r76w-gfvq-4v99.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0804.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990607.data","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0546.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0499","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0772","title":"康柏 Insight Management Agent 长字符串拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Compaq Management Agents和Compaq Survey Utility存在拒绝服务漏洞，由于程序对输入数据缺乏充分的长度校验，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络向目标系统的2301端口发送超长字符串，触发服务异常崩溃或系统无响应。该漏洞影响运行Compaq Insight Management Agent及相关管理代理服务的服务器系统，攻击条件简单，仅需目标端口网络可达即可实施利用，无需任何凭据，导致合法用户无法正常访问管理服务，影响系统可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0772"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.590","remediation":"升级 Compaq Insight Management Agent 及 Survey Utility 至 Compaq 官方发布的修复版本，或安装对应 SoftPaq 安全补丁；如暂无法升级，应在防火墙或主机 ACL 中限制仅允许可信管理网段访问 TCP 2301 端口，并临时禁用不必要的 Compaq Survey Utility 服务以降低被攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0772","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7cda0b7fa75f17f1e2b56ef076a6f9175f854ab4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0772.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0772","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0772.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4cacb08131e7c4736ad136de17873dbcaeddf850/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0772.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-545v-66g8-w7vj/GHSA-545v-66g8-w7vj.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0772.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000656.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1130","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1130.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1485","title":"SGI IRIX nsd 信息泄露漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.5 至 6.5.2 版本的 nsd 组件存在信息泄露漏洞。nsd 在 UDP 端口上导出一个虚拟文件系统，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过挂载该虚拟文件系统，读取目标系统上的任意文件，并可能引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.5、6.5.1 及 6.5.2 版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1485"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.550","remediation":"建议升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5.3 或更高版本（如 6.5.30），该版本已修复 nsd 虚拟文件系统导出漏洞；如无法立即升级，请立即停用并禁用 nsd 服务（/etc/init.d/nsd stop && chkconfig nsd off），并在边界防火墙屏蔽 nsd 使用的 UDP 端口（通常为 2049/NFS 相关端口）以防止远程挂载和信息泄露，同时监控异常 UDP 流量作为临时缓解措施。必须升级至修复版本彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92818552106912&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/8564","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/412","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2246","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2247","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19316","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1485.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1485.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1485","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1485.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1485.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gph4-8wj3-3mgr/GHSA-gph4-8wj3-3mgr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1485.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b806245e-5163-48ad-8c76-8f42a7ab790e.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1130.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0802","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9107,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10793}}","description":"Internet Explorer 5 的收藏夹图标（Favorites icon）处理功能存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当浏览器解析攻击者构造的畸形收藏夹图标文件时，由于未对输入数据长度进行正确边界校验，会导致缓冲区溢出，使远程攻击者能够在目标用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响使用 Internet Explorer 5 的 Windows 系统，攻击者可借助恶意网页或诱导用户导入特制收藏夹图标的方式触发，无需身份认证，只要受害者访问恶意内容即可实现远程代码执行，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0802"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.283","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 SP2 或 IE 5.5 及以上版本，并安装微软 2000 年 3 月安全汇总补丁（如 Windows Update 中的 IE 累积更新）。如暂无法升级，可在浏览器安全设置中将「收藏夹」及 Active Desktop 相关脚本禁用，并通过代理过滤畸形 Favorites 图标(.ico)响应作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231450","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-018","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0802.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0802.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0802.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0802","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0802.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0802.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0802.md","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/9ddbd359f5d34d4a30a937d3247f869d55e5f670/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-08xx/CVE-1999-0802.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/6aa4dba00ee770284d0dfd313876db0eed616986/1999/CVE-1999-0802.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0802.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0467","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0467.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0755","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RAS 拨号网络密码缓存漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 及其 SP1 至 SP5 版本的远程访问服务（RAS）与路由和远程访问服务（RRAS）客户端存在密码缓存缺陷。当用户通过拨号网络连接进行登录时，系统会在用户并未勾选\"保存密码\"选项的情况下，仍将用户的登录密码缓存在本地。这意味着任何能够访问该主机的本地用户，都可能在未经授权的情况下读取到此前连接所用凭据，进而导致敏感账户信息的泄露。该漏洞影响范围涵盖上述所有受影响的 Windows NT 4.0 系统版本，攻击条件为攻击者需具备对目标主机的本地访问权限，利用方式则是直接读取系统缓存中已存储的明文或可逆密码数据。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0755"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.367","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 于 1999 年 5 月发布的安全更新 MS99-017 补丁，该补丁修复了 RAS/RRAS 客户端无论是否勾选\"保存密码\"选项都会缓存凭据的问题。补丁适用于 Windows NT 4.0 Workstation、Server 及 Enterprise Edition。如无法安装补丁，可启用 SYSKEY 功能（Windows NT 4.0 SP4 及以上）对注册表中存储的密码数据进行强加密作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ230681","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-017","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19196","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0755.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0755.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0755","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/76af88afbb282d6c9e8ce3b9f6942bcb7e39be57/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0755.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0755.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g6q4-7rrm-ppv6/GHSA-g6q4-7rrm-ppv6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0755.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0467.toml"}]